---

<Layout title="Swiss Paraglide Zermatt - Tandem Paragliding Flights in front of the Matterhorn.">
	<main>
		
      <div class="bg-white">
        <div class="mx-auto max-w-2xl px-4 py-24 sm:px-6 sm:py-32 lg:max-w-7xl lg:px-8">
          <div class="max-w-3xl">
            <h1 id="features-heading" class="font-medium text-gray-700">Pre-flight</h1>
            <h2 class="mt-2 text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight text-gray-900 sm:text-4xl">
              Good to know before you book a flight with Swiss Paraglide Zermatt.
            </h2>
            <p class="mt-4 text-gray-700">
               General information for your tandem paragliding flight in Zermatt. This will help you to prepare for your flight and to know what to expect.
               Safety is our top priority, and wind/weather conditions along with the fitness and confidence of the passenger all play a role our the decision to fly.
            </p>
          </div>
      
          <div class="mt-11 grid grid-cols-1 items-start gap-x-6 gap-y-16 sm:mt-16 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 lg:gap-x-8    text-sm font-light text-black">


            <div class="flex flex-col-reverse">
              <div class="mt-6">
                <h3 class="text-xl font-medium drop-shadow-md">
                  Weather
                </h3>
                <p class="mt-2 ">
                  We handle providing you with a safe and enjoyable flight &ndash; you're in charge of organising the beautiful
                  flying weather :-)
                </p>
                <p class="mt-2 ">
                  It goes without saying that Paragliding is absolutely, utterly weather dependant &ndash; the Weather Gods
                  are in charge.
                  If we are not able to fly due to poor weather conditions, you will not be charged for the Paragliding. 
                </p>
              </div>
              <div class="aspect-h-1 aspect-w-1 overflow-hidden rounded-lg bg-gray-100">
                <svg class="p-8" width="32" height="32" viewBox="0 -960 960 960" fill="currentColor" aria-hidden="true" focusable="false" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill-rule="evenodd" clip-rule="evenodd">
