                </svg>
              </div>
            </div>

            
            <div class="flex flex-col-reverse">
              <div class="mt-6">
                <h3 class="text-xl font-medium drop-shadow-md">
                  Fitness
                </h3>
                <p class="mt-2 ">
                  You need to be good on your feet and able to run 10-20 steps with confidence on the start! It's particularly important that you 
                  follow the pilot's instructions at the take off (it's easy, but your pilot can't run for you). 
                </p>
                <p class="mt-2 ">
                  If you are older, heavier and/or have physical issues that affect being able to run, then please 
                  let us know &ndash; we will do our best, but as always, safety first! 
                </p>
              </div>
              <div class="aspect-h-1 aspect-w-1 overflow-hidden rounded-lg bg-gray-100">
                <svg class="p-8" width="32" height="32" viewBox="0 -960 960 960" fill="currentColor" aria-hidden="true" focusable="false" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill-rule="evenodd" clip-rule="evenodd">
